Vista Land Advances Most in Five Weeks After Buying Back Shares

-- B y   I a n   S a y s o n
-- 
2011-09-16T03:21:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/vista-land-advances-most-in-five-weeks-after-buying-back-shares.html
Vista Land & Lifescapes Inc. (VLL) 
climbed the most in five weeks in Manila trading after the
Philippine developer said it bought back 13.55 million shares.
The stock increased 4 percent to 3.12 pesos as of 11:08 a.m.
local time, heading for the sharpest gain since Aug. 10.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Ian Sayson in Manila at 
